PhonePe Pulse Dashboard | Power BI Project
📌 Project Overview
This project is an interactive Power BI dashboard developed using PhonePe Pulse data to analyze India's digital payment ecosystem. The dashboard transforms raw transaction data into meaningful insights by visualizing transaction trends, user growth, and state-wise digital payment adoption across India.
🎯 Objectives
Analyze transaction volume and transaction value across states.
Track digital payment growth over different years and quarters.
Compare registered users and app opens across regions.
Identify top-performing states and emerging digital payment trends.
Build an interactive dashboard for data-driven decision-making.
📊 Dashboard Features
Total Transactions & Total Transaction Amount KPIs
State-wise transaction analysis
Quarterly and yearly trend analysis
Registered users and app opens analysis
Top 10 states comparison
Interactive maps, filters, and slicers
Dynamic visualizations for better insights
🛠️ Tech Stack
Power BI
DAX
Power Query
Excel/CSV
PhonePe Pulse Dataset
